    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"About\"\ncss: about_styles_css.css\n---\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n<script>\n// Simple scrollytelling for background map\ndocument.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {\n  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n    entries.forEach((entry) => {\n      if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n        // Remove active class from all steps\n        document.querySelectorAll('.step').forEach(step => {\n          step.classList.remove('active');\n        });\n        \n        // Add active class to current step\n        entry.target.classList.add('active');\n        \n        // Update map\n        if (typeof window.updateMapStep === 'function') {\n          window.updateMapStep(entry.target.id);\n        }\n      }\n    });\n  }, {\n    threshold: 0.6\n  });\n\n  // Observe all steps\n  document.querySelectorAll('.step').forEach(step => {\n    observer.observe(step);\n  });\n});\n</script>\n:::\n\n\n::: intro-section\nI'm Kylie, an Atlanta-native (technically Decatur), crazy dog lady, runner, and science nerd. I work as an infectious disease modeller, meaning that I use math, stats, and R to study the spread of diseases and how interventions, like vaccines, can impact that spread. My career path has taken me from Atlanta to London, Amsterdam, Hong Kong, and soon to Melbourne. I love to explore both near and far, whether that's through research collaborations, weekend hikes, discovering local coffee shops, or finding the best running trails in each new city.\n\nScroll through my journey below and watch it unfold on the map.\n:::\n\n### My Journey\n\n::::::::::::::: scrolly-container\n::::::::::::: scrolly-content\n<!-- ::: {.step #step-intro} -->\n\n<!-- ### 🌍 A Global Adventure -->\n\n<!-- Scroll through my journey as it unfolds across the map. Each step of my career has taken me to new places and opened new opportunities. -->\n\n<!-- ::: -->\n\n:::: {#step-atlanta .step}\n### 🎓 PhD\n\n::: step-year\n2011-2018\n:::\n\nI did my PhD at Emory University in Atlanta, GA. Georgia will always be home, but the world was calling!\n::::\n\n:::: {#step-london .step}\n### 🇬🇧 Postdoc\n\n::: step-year\n2018-2020\n:::\n\nMoved to London for a postdoc at Imperial College London.\n::::\n\n:::: {#step-amsterdam .step}\n### 🇳🇱 Senior Researcher\n\n::: step-year\n2020-2025\n:::\n\nDuring the pandemic, I relocated to Amsterdam and joined the RIVM as a senior researcher in infectious disease modelling. Found my niche in modelling for public health policy.\n::::\n\n:::: {#step-hongkong .step}\n### 🇭🇰 Honorary Assistant Professor\n\n::: step-year\n2022-Present\n:::\n\nJoined University of Hong Kong School of Public Health as Honorary Assistant Professor, expanding international research collaborations and working on real-world vaccine effectiveness.\n::::\n\n:::: {#step-melbourne .step}\n### 🇦🇺 Modelling for Policy Lead\n\n::: step-year\n2025-Present\n:::\n\nStarted a new position at the Peter Doherty Institute for Infectious and Immunity at the University of Melbourne in October 2025! 🦘\n::::\n:::::::::::::\n\n::: scrolly-map\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"leaflet html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-26279ffe8531bfe2ec3a\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-26279ffe8531bfe2ec3a\">{\"x\":{\"options\":{\"crs\":{\"crsClass\":\"L.CRS.EPSG3857\",\"code\":null,\"proj4def\":null,\"projectedBounds\":null,\"options\":{}}},\"calls\":[{\"method\":\"addProviderTiles\",\"args\":[\"CartoDB.Positron\",null,null,{\"errorTileUrl\":\"\",\"noWrap\":false,\"detectRetina\":false}]}],\"setView\":[[20,30],2,[]]},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":{\"render\":[{\"code\":\"function(el, x, data) {\\n  return (\\nfunction(el, x) {\\n  window.journeyMap = this;\\n  \\n  // Disable map interaction\\n  this.dragging.disable();\\n  this.touchZoom.disable();\\n  this.doubleClickZoom.disable();\\n  this.scrollWheelZoom.disable();\\n  this.boxZoom.disable();\\n  this.keyboard.disable();\\n  if (this.tap) this.tap.disable();\\n  \\n  // Locations with optimized zoom levels for smooth transitions\\n  window.locations = {\\n    atlanta: {lng: -84.296, lat: 33.749, zoom: 6},\\n    london: {lng: -0.1276, lat: 51.5074, zoom: 6},\\n    amsterdam: {lng: 4.9041, lat: 52.3676, zoom: 6},\\n    hongkong: {lng: 114.1694, lat: 22.3193, zoom: 5},\\n    melbourne: {lng: 144.9631, lat: -37.8136, zoom: 6},\\n    overview: {lng: 30, lat: 20, zoom: 2}\\n  };\\n  \\n  window.currentMarkers = [];\\n  \\n  // Enhanced marker creation with better styling\\n  var createMarker = function(lat, lng, popup, isPrimary) {\\n    var size = isPrimary ? 28 : 18;\\n    var color = isPrimary ? '#2DD4BF' : '#A7F3D0';\\n    var pulseAnim = isPrimary ? 'animation: pulse 2s infinite;' : '';\\n    \\n    var icon = L.divIcon({\\n      html: '<div style=\\\"background: ' + color + '; width: ' + size + 'px; height: ' + size + 'px; border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid #FFFFFF; box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45,212,191,0.5); ' + pulseAnim + '\\\"><\\/div><style>@keyframes pulse { 0% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45,212,191,0.5); } 50% { transform: scale(1.15); box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(45,212,191,0.7); } 100% { transform: scale(1); box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(45,212,191,0.5); } }<\\/style>',\\n      iconSize: [size, size],\\n      className: 'journey-marker'\\n    });\\n    \\n    var marker = L.marker([lat, lng], {icon: icon}).bindPopup(popup, {\\n      className: 'custom-popup'\\n    });\\n    window.currentMarkers.push(marker);\\n    return marker;\\n  };\\n  \\n  // Smooth transition function\\n  var smoothFlyTo = function(lat, lng, zoom) {\\n    window.journeyMap.flyTo([lat, lng], zoom, {\\n      animate: true,\\n      duration: 2.5,\\n      easeLinearity: 0.1\\n    });\\n  };\\n  \\n  window.updateMapStep = function(stepId) {\\n    var map = window.journeyMap;\\n    \\n    // Clear everything and rebuild to ensure proper primary/secondary states\\n    window.currentMarkers.forEach(function(marker) {\\n      map.removeLayer(marker);\\n    });\\n    window.currentMarkers = [];\\n    \\n    map.eachLayer(function(layer) {\\n      if (layer._latlngs) {\\n        map.removeLayer(layer);\\n      }\\n    });\\n    \\n    switch(stepId) {\\n      case 'step-atlanta':\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, window.locations.atlanta.zoom);\\n        setTimeout(function() {\\n          createMarker(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Atlanta, GA<\\/strong><br>PhD at Emory University<br>(2011-2018)', true).addTo(map);\\n        }, 1000);\\n        break;\\n        \\n      case 'step-london':\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng, window.locations.london.zoom);\\n        setTimeout(function() {\\n          // Add previous markers (dimmed) and current (primary)\\n          createMarker(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Atlanta, GA<\\/strong><br>PhD completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng, \\n                      '<strong>London, UK<\\/strong><br>Postdoc at Imperial College<br>(2018-2020)', true).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add journey line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#2DD4BF', weight: 4, opacity: 0.8}).addTo(map);\\n        }, 1000);\\n        break;\\n        \\n      case 'step-amsterdam':\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng, window.locations.amsterdam.zoom);\\n        setTimeout(function() {\\n          // Add all previous markers (dimmed) and current (primary)\\n          createMarker(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Atlanta, GA<\\/strong><br>PhD completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng, \\n                      '<strong>London, UK<\\/strong><br>Postdoc completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Amsterdam, NL<\\/strong><br>Senior Researcher at RIVM<br>(2020-Present)', true).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add complete journey line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng],\\n                     [window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#2DD4BF', weight: 4, opacity: 0.8}).addTo(map);\\n        }, 1000);\\n        break;\\n        \\n      case 'step-hongkong':\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.hongkong.lat, window.locations.hongkong.lng, window.locations.hongkong.zoom);\\n        setTimeout(function() {\\n          // Add all previous markers\\n          createMarker(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Atlanta, GA<\\/strong><br>PhD completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng, \\n                      '<strong>London, UK<\\/strong><br>Postdoc completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Amsterdam, NL<\\/strong><br>Home base at RIVM', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.hongkong.lat, window.locations.hongkong.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Hong Kong<\\/strong><br>Honorary Assistant Professor<br>University of Hong Kong<br>(2022-Present)', true).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add main journey line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng],\\n                     [window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#2DD4BF', weight: 4, opacity: 0.8}).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add collaboration line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.hongkong.lat, window.locations.hongkong.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#14B8A6', weight: 3, opacity: 0.7, dashArray: '10,5'}).addTo(map);\\n        }, 1000);\\n        break;\\n        \\n      case 'step-melbourne':\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.melbourne.lat, window.locations.melbourne.lng, window.locations.melbourne.zoom);\\n        setTimeout(function() {\\n          // Add all previous markers\\n          createMarker(window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Atlanta, GA<\\/strong><br>PhD completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng, \\n                      '<strong>London, UK<\\/strong><br>Postdoc completed', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Amsterdam, NL<\\/strong><br>Current position at RIVM', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.hongkong.lat, window.locations.hongkong.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Hong Kong<\\/strong><br>Ongoing collaboration', false).addTo(map);\\n          createMarker(window.locations.melbourne.lat, window.locations.melbourne.lng, \\n                      '<strong>Melbourne, AU<\\/strong><br>University of Melbourne<br>Modelling for Policy Lead<br>(Coming Soon!)', true).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add main journey line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.atlanta.lat, window.locations.atlanta.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.london.lat, window.locations.london.lng],\\n                     [window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#2DD4BF', weight: 4, opacity: 0.8}).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add collaboration line\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.hongkong.lat, window.locations.hongkong.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#14B8A6', weight: 3, opacity: 0.7, dashArray: '10,5'}).addTo(map);\\n          \\n          // Add future connection\\n          L.polyline([[window.locations.amsterdam.lat, window.locations.amsterdam.lng], \\n                     [window.locations.melbourne.lat, window.locations.melbourne.lng]], \\n                     {color: '#5EEAD4', weight: 3, opacity: 0.6, dashArray: '15,8'}).addTo(map);\\n        }, 1000);\\n        break;\\n        \\n      default:\\n        smoothFlyTo(window.locations.overview.lat, window.locations.overview.lng, window.locations.overview.zoom);\\n        break;\\n    }\\n  };\\n}\\n).call(this.getMap(), el, x, data);\\n}\",\"data\":null}]}}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n:::\n:::::::::::::::\n\n<!-- Get stats -->\n\n<!-- Google scholar ID: gfJENK8AAAAJ -->\n\n\n\n### Quick Stats\n\n:::::::::::::::::::::: outro-section\n::::::::::::::::::::: stats-grid\n::::: stat-card\n::: {#km-stat .stat-number}\n15,096.7\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nKilometers Run\n:::\n:::::\n\n::::: stat-card\n::: {#countries-stat .stat-number}\n37\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nCountries Visited\n:::\n:::::\n\n::::: stat-card\n::: {#pub-stat .stat-number}\n101\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nGoogle Scholar Publications\n:::\n:::::\n\n::::: stat-card\n::: stat-number\n17,352\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nTotal Citations\n:::\n:::::\n\n::::: stat-card\n::: {#books-stat .stat-number}\n25\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nBooks Read This Year\n:::\n:::::\n\n::::: stat-card\n::: {#leon-stat .stat-number}\n4\n:::\n\n::: stat-label\nDaily dog walks with Leon\n:::\n:::::\n:::::::::::::::::::::\n::::::::::::::::::::::\n\n### Life Outside of Research\n\n:::::::::: outro-section\n::::::::: photo-grid\n::: photo-card\n![](photos/leon.jpeg) **Leon** - My pretty princess 👑\n:::\n\n::: photo-card\n[![](photos/running.jpeg)](https://www.strava.com/athletes/37546778) **Running** - Still my favorite way to explore\n:::\n\n::: photo-card\n![](photos/kylie_redwoods.jpeg) **Hiking** - Redwoods National & State Parks\n:::\n\n::: photo-card\n[![](photos/cooking.jpeg)](https://www.instagram.com/goinginforthekale/) **Cooking** - Food adventures on Instagram\n:::\n\n::: photo-card\n![](photos/coffee.jpeg) **Coffee** - Perfecting my homemade flat white (my latte art needs work) 🙃\n:::\n\n::: photo-card\n[![](images/rladies_amsterdam_logo.png)](https://www.meetup.com/rladies-amsterdam/) **R Ladies Amsterdam** - Volunteer Organizer\n\nFollow on [BlueSky](https://bsky.app/profile/rladiesamsterdam.bsky.social)\n:::\n:::::::::\n\nI continue to find any excuse to hop on a plane, train, or automobile and explore new places. Whether it's for research collaborations, conferences, or just weekend adventures, I believe that travel enriches both personal and professional perspectives. With an upcoming move to Melbourne on the horizon, the adventure continues!\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n*Want to connect?* Find me on social media or drop me an email - I'm always happy to chat about research, travel recommendations, the perfect flat white recipe, or tips for international moves!\n::::::::::\n",
